Enum NotTerminal

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<NotTerminal>
      • NotTerminal
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<NotTerminal>

    public enum NotTerminal
extends java.lang.Enum<NotTerminal>
    The goal of this class is to enumerate the list of None-terminal variables that are in our grammar. We indeed use that list to build the parsetree
